Class WaitingListEntry

java.lang.Object
common.WaitingListEntry
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class WaitingListEntry extends Object implements Serializable
Represents a customer on the restaurant's waiting list. This class tracks entries for diners who could not find an immediate reservation.
